{"tid":653900,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過Belize？","createTime":"2018-05-05T06:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T17:40:02.000Z","uid":15965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47975f4a8ad1b75889576f59d9a35238a2164660","tid":653900,"uid":15965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"可唔可以Share下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c1c9c5466e575bf3eabdc77fbc5cd6dd314d5","tid":653900,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"想去幾多日?<br />\n首都Belmopan細到好似鄉村咁<br />\nBelize City多華人不過治安麻麻<br />\n通常一係去外島玩浮潛<br />\n一係去San Ignacio,<br />\n果度附近有d Maya Site<br />\n去完果度就可以順手過去危地馬拉<br />\nTikal好近果度"},{"pid":"170acb6c5321fffcd2f6346befe541df852510a9","tid":653900,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"有，只去過幾日Caye Caulker，覺得好歎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個島做遊客生意，hostel同平價酒店為主，浮潛記住幫襯Caveman，態度同環境一流，魔鬼魚甚至海龜都見到，水亦好暖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n島上面有間做中餐外賣，成個島入面算最平，亦有幾檔華人雜貨店，講廣東話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19006c1d781807f26652b50b909ec4c57d2c51f1","tid":653900,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"有親戚移民左去!<br />\n佢話好多美國鬼成日去潛水"},{"pid":"d344433af1466bcfb789fe49a635749445a3b404","tid":653900,"uid":15965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"我應該去San Pedro潛水同坐飛機睇藍洞<br />\n之後留一日Caye Caulker<br />\n<br />\n有無咩好食/好玩推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99510034c4b1aed19d04a3a54e7b5e1e5c97735","tid":653900,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"去過san pedro同caye caulker。個人黎講覺得overrated，又貴又無想像中咁靚。"},{"pid":"c21affb68db4321b832e739fd87678b91b93f690","tid":653900,"uid":7458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n想移民去果度"},{"pid":"e8a0338c09e21b0f5579cf6eed2ea661e1446019","tid":653900,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"百力滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60caf77c5d55db77e09287a8d8e5939717bdbfbc","tid":653900,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"食都係食龍蝦<br />\n嗰度d華人超多都係台山人<br />\n識講廣東話<br />\nd中餐館中式炒飯都幾似香港<br />\n<br />\n其實伯利兹d maya site<br />\n無危地馬拉同埋墨西哥咁出名<br />\n不過睇頭一d都唔輸<br />\n<br />\n治安都係夜晚小心d<br />\n物價貴香港少少"}]}